{
  "id": "git-worktrees-claude-code",
  "title": "Git Worktrees en Claude Code",
  "description": "Cómo usar git worktrees para trabajar en múltiples ramas de forma completamente aislada sin interrumpir tu sesión actual",
  "theme": "linea-directa",
  "fps": 30,
  "width": 1280,
  "height": 720,
  "scenes": [
    {
      "type": "intro",
      "title": "Git Worktrees en Claude Code",
      "subtitle": "Trabaja en ramas paralelas sin perder contexto",
      "durationInSeconds": 4
    },
    {
      "type": "terminal",
      "title": "Crear un worktree aislado",
      "lines": [
        {
          "kind": "command",
          "text": "> EnterWorktree  (name: \"feature-auth\")",
          "delayAfterMs": 800
        },
        {
          "kind": "output",
          "text": "Created worktree at .claude/worktrees/feature-auth"
        },
        {
          "kind": "output",
          "text": "Branch: worktree-feature-auth — session is now isolated",
          "delayAfterMs": 400
        },
        {
          "kind": "blank",
          "text": ""
        },
        {
          "kind": "command",
          "text": "$ git worktree list",
          "delayAfterMs": 600
        },
        {
          "kind": "output",
          "text": "/project                          8d07f65 [main]"
        },
        {
          "kind": "output",
          "text": "/project/.claude/worktrees/feature-auth  8d07f65 [worktree-feature-auth]"
        },
        {
          "kind": "blank",
          "text": "",
          "delayAfterMs": 400
        },
        {
          "kind": "claude",
          "text": "Ahora trabajamos en una rama aislada. Los cambios aquí no afectan a main."
        }
      ],
      "durationInSeconds": 12
    },
    {
      "type": "callout",
      "text": "Ideal para revisar un bug en producción mientras desarrollas una feature — sin stash, sin commits temporales.",
      "position": "bottom",
      "background": "overlay",
      "durationInSeconds": 4
    },
    {
      "type": "terminal",
      "title": "Salir del worktree",
      "lines": [
        {
          "kind": "command",
          "text": "> ExitWorktree  (action: \"keep\")",
          "delayAfterMs": 700
        },
        {
          "kind": "output",
          "text": "Exited worktree. Branch worktree-feature-auth preserved."
        },
        {
          "kind": "output",
          "text": "Session restored to /project [main]",
          "delayAfterMs": 300
        },
        {
          "kind": "blank",
          "text": "",
          "delayAfterMs": 600
        },
        {
          "kind": "command",
          "text": "> ExitWorktree  (action: \"remove\")",
          "delayAfterMs": 700
        },
        {
          "kind": "output",
          "text": "Exited and removed worktree + branch worktree-feature-auth."
        },
        {
          "kind": "claude",
          "text": "\"keep\" conserva la rama para continuar después. \"remove\" limpia todo al salir.",
          "delayAfterMs": 400
        }
      ],
      "durationInSeconds": 10
    },
    {
      "type": "outro",
      "title": "Git Worktrees: Lo esencial",
      "bullets": [
        "EnterWorktree crea una rama aislada desde HEAD en .claude/worktrees/",
        "ExitWorktree(keep) preserva la rama · ExitWorktree(remove) la elimina",
        "Cada worktree tiene su propio CWD, memoria y contexto de sesión",
        "Úsalo cuando el usuario mencione explícitamente \"worktree\""
      ],
      "durationInSeconds": 6
    }
  ]
}
